Fresh Pi session: MAKE THE SELECTED SCENARIO GREEN, OPTIONALLY REFACTOR, AND UPDATE THE INVENTORY.

Inputs:
- Selected scenario: latest {{run.dir}}/tdd/current-scenario-*.json
- Deterministic red report: latest {{run.dir}}/tdd/red-verification-*.md
- Latest scenario list: latest JSON under {{run.dir}}/test-list/
- Constraints: {{run.dir}}/design/repository-constraints.md
- Worktree: {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Implement only the selected behavior, preserve accumulated behavior, and leave one coherent committed green increment.

Rules:
- Make the smallest production change that satisfies the selected test.
- Do not delete, skip, or weaken tests or derive expected values from implementation output without independent justification.
- Run the focused command and relevant prior checks while working.
- Refactor only after green and only when it materially improves the changed code; behavior must remain unchanged.
- Record newly discovered behavior in discoveries. Add only distinct, in-scope discoveries to the scenario list, which must never exceed eight entries.
- Mark only the selected scenario `complete`, with its focused manifest/report as evidence. Preserve `regression-covered` classifications.
- Preserve the prepared snapshot and write the current round's authoritative `-final` snapshot.
- Commit the coherent test and implementation increment locally after it is green. Do not push or create a PR.

Write:
- Summary, including implementation and any refactor decision: {{run.dir}}/tdd/green-summary-{{run.round}}.md
- Discoveries: {{run.dir}}/tdd/discovered-scenarios-{{run.round}}.json
- Updated snapshot: {{run.dir}}/test-list/scenarios-{{run.round}}-final.json
- Status: {{run.dir}}/tdd/green-status-{{run.round}}.json
- Current actionable issues on failure only: {{run.dir}}/tdd/green-issues-{{run.round}}.json

Discovery shape:
{"scenarios":[{"description":"...","expected_behavior":"...","source":"implement-green"}]}

Statuses:
{"status":"pass","summary":"selected behavior is green and committed","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"current green increment remains incomplete","issues_file":"tdd/green-issues-{{run.round}}.json"}
